race.comment: BETTER BE READY (1) goes well for rider Cormack who has two wins and two seconds from just four rides and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside marble. Racing high on confidence of late and should be right there at the business end. CONVERTOR (2) has a handy record over this course and distance with a win and five placings from just seven starts. Rates a genuine top-three contender on best form. INNOVATES (5) has just run into one better at the past couple and looks ready for the step-up to the mile now. In the mix. GRUMPYWANTSATISSUE (10) shed the maiden tag last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Can go right on with the job now. AL RAS BLUES (4) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
